#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware.rst:65
msgid ""
"If you do not have a numeric Numpad on the side of your keyboard, you may want to "
"emulate one (uses the numbers at the top of the keyboard instead, however, removes "
"quick access to layer visibility)."
msgstr ""
"如果你的键盘没有数字键区，你可能得开启模拟选项(使用上方的数字键代替，不过，这样就不"
"能使用快捷键切换图层了)。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware.rst:71
