#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware.rst:75
msgid "Non-English Keyboards"
msgstr "非英文键盘"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware.rst:77
msgid ""
"If you use a keyboard with a non-English keyboard layout, you still may benefit "
"from switching your computer to the UK or US layout as long as you work with "
"Blender."
msgstr "如果你用的是非英文布局的键盘，你可能还得切换为UK或US布局才能使用Blender工作。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware.rst:82
msgid ""
"You can also change the default keymap and default hotkeys from the :doc:`User "
"Preferences </preferences/input>`, however, this manual assumes you are using the "
"default keymap."
msgstr ""
"还可以在 :doc:`用户设置 </preferences/input>` 修改默认的键位映射和默认快捷键，不过，"
"本手册会假定你用的是默认键位映射。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware.rst:92
msgid ""
"Graphics tablets can be used to provide a more traditional method of controlling "
"the mouse cursor using a pen. This can help to provide a more familiar experience "
"for artists who are used to painting and drawing with similar tools, as well as "
"provide additional controls such as pressure sensitivity."
msgstr ""
"因为数位板有笔这个元素，所以使用它可以用更为传统的方式控制鼠标指针，这对习惯用笔工作"
"的艺术工作者来说是个利好消息，而且数位板还能提供压感等参数。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware.rst:99
msgid ""
"If you are using a graphic tablet instead of a mouse and pressure sensitivity does "
"not work properly, try to place the mouse pointer in the Blender window and then "
"unplug/replug your graphic tablet. This might help."
msgstr ""
"如果你用数位板代替鼠标工作的时候，发现数位板的压感不正常，你可以试着先把指针放置在"
"Blender界面中，再把数位板的线头拔出来吹吹灰插回去，这也许能管用。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware.rst:106
msgid "3D Mice"
msgstr "3D 鼠标"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/configuration/hardware.rst:108
msgid ""
"3D Mice or :abbr:`NDOF (N-Degrees of Freedom)` devices are hardware that you can "
"use to navigate a scene in Blender. Currently only devices made by 3Dconnexion are "
"supported. These devices allow you to explore a scene, as well as :ref:`Walk/Fly "
"modes <3dview-walk-fly>`."
msgstr ""
"3D鼠标或者 :abbr:`NDOF (N-Degrees of Freedom)` 设备是用于在Blender中浏览视图的硬件。"
"目前仅支持3Dconnexion的硬件。这些硬件可以浏览场景， 也可以使用 :ref:`行走/飞行模式 "
"<3dview-walk-fly>`。"

